pound interest is real. Yep. Thank you, my friend. You're wonderful. Have a good day. You can't take no for an answer. You know that, right? Oh, no, no, no. Thank you, sir. Appreciate you, man. Have a great day.",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.6,
      "text": "Excuse me, sir. Sir, how did you get rich?"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.2,
      "end": 3.7,
      "text": "Do you know me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 4.0,
      "end": 5.3,
      "text": "Sir, how did you get rich?"
    },
    {
      "start": 5.5,
      "end": 6.3,
      "text": "Do you know these people?"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.6,
      "end": 8.8,
      "text": "You look like money, man. I see the slick back white hair."
    },
    {
      "start": 9.2,
      "end": 12.1,
      "text": "How the fuck did you pick him out out of the three of us?"
    },
    {
      "start": 12.2,
      "end": 13.6,
      "text": "Do I look fucking broke?"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.1,
      "end": 15.0,
      "text": "Who's the richest one here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 15.1,
      "end": 15.5,
      "text": "He is."
    },
    {
      "start": 15.6,
      "end": 15.8,
      "text": "He is."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.0,
      "end": 16.4,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.5,
      "end": 17.1,
      "text": "You got it, Rick."
    },
    {
      "start": 17.3,
      "end": 17.8,
      "text": "Real quick, sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 17.9,
      "end": 19.5,
      "text": "So I have a channel with 21 million followers."
    },
    {
      "start": 19.8,
      "end": 22.0,
      "text": "I've interviewed 44 billionaires in the last four years."
    },
    {
      "start": 22.1,
      "end": 23.2,
      "text": "Well, I had a business where you went."
    },
    {
      "start": 23.2,
      "end": 23.9,
      "text": "Oh, I'll show you guys."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.0,
      "end": 24.9,
      "text": "So you were in the money business."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.2,
      "end": 25.8,
      "text": "Oh, it's bond trader."
    },
    {
      "start": 26.1,
      "end": 27.5,
      "text": "So what did you learn about investing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 27.8,
      "end": 29.6,
      "text": "The most important thing is, in my opinion,"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.6,
      "end": 30.6,
      "text": "it was always to be confident."
    },
    {
      "start": 30.8,
      "end": 32.9,
      "text": "Because every day, even when I had bad days, a bad week,"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.0,
      "end": 33.9,
      "text": "I was always confident."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.0,
      "end": 34.9,
      "text": "I couldn't wait to get to work."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.9,
      "end": 36.1,
      "text": "That's the most important thing in the world."
    },
    {
      "start": 36.2,
      "end": 37.1,
      "text": "Did you come from a lot of money?"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.4,
      "end": 37.9,
      "text": "No. Zero."
    },
    {
      "start": 38.2,
      "end": 39.6,
      "text": "So what was your turning point to financial freedom?"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.8,
      "end": 41.3,
      "text": "I thought, and I made my first million,"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.5,
      "end": 42.9,
      "text": "I thought I achieved something really wonderful."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.1,
      "end": 43.6,
      "text": "How old were you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.7,
      "end": 44.0,
      "text": "28."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.2,
      "end": 45.9,
      "text": "What would you say was the most amount of money"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.9,
      "end": 46.9,
      "text": "you made in a single year?"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.0,
      "end": 47.3,
      "text": "For myself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.6,
      "end": 47.8,
      "text": "Yes, sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 48.0,
      "end": 48.3,
      "text": "15?"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.6,
      "end": 49.1,
      "text": "15 what?"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.4,
      "end": 49.5,
      "text": "A million."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.7,
      "end": 50.3,
      "text": "$15 million."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.6,
      "end": 51.4,
      "text": "That's way back then."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.5,
      "end": 53.7,
      "text": "But how did you scale your income from one to 15 million?"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.8,
      "end": 54.6,
      "text": "Tell me that real quick."
    },
    {
      "start": 54.9,
      "end": 56.3,
      "text": "So last two, I promise you this is it."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.5,
      "end": 57.8,
      "text": "This is to help the younger generation."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.2,
      "end": 61.4,
      "text": "Every kid should be involved."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.6,
      "end": 63.0,
      "text": "They should be invested into the stock market."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.2,
      "end": 64.2,
      "text": "Well, how do you know what stocks to buy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.4,
      "end": 64.5,
      "text": "You don't."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.7,
      "end": 66.6,
      "text": "You buy the S&P 500, and that's all you need to know."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.6,
      "end": 67.5,
      "text": "That's all you did right there?"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.6,
      "end": 69.6,
      "text": "It's one ETF or one fund, and that's it."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.7,
      "end": 71.2,
      "text": "Did you blow a lot of money when you were coming up?"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.4,
      "end": 71.5,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.7,
      "end": 72.0,
      "text": "You did?"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.3,
      "end": 72.7,
      "text": "No regrets."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.0,
      "end": 74.7,
      "text": "Last message to the younger generation right here."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.8,
      "end": 76.1,
      "text": "One more piece of advice you got."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.2,
      "end": 76.5,
      "text": "One more thing."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.5,
      "end": 77.1,
      "text": "Invest early."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.5,
      "end": 78.3,
      "text": "Invest confidently."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.7,
      "end": 79.3,
      "text": "Don't speculate."
    },
    {
      "start": 79.6,
      "end": 80.9,
      "text": "Just buy the S&P 500."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.1,
      "end": 83.8,
      "text": "For the last 100 years, it's returned 10% a year on average."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.0,
      "end": 84.8,
      "text": "10% a year."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.1,
      "end": 85.7,
      "text": "Triples in 12."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.2,
      "end": 87.1,
      "text": "Quadruples in 15."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.4,
      "end": 88.5,
      "text": "The compound interest is real."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.8,
      "end": 88.9,
      "text": "Yep."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.9,
      "end": 89.7,
      "text": "Thank you, my friend."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.8,
      "end": 90.2,
      "text": "You're wonderful."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.5,
      "end": 91.0,
      "text": "Have a good day."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.5,
      "end": 92.5,
      "text": "You can't take no for an answer."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.6,
      "end": 93.1,
      "text": "You know that, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.3,
      "end": 93.9,
      "text": "Oh, no, no, no."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.1,
      "end": 94.4,
      "text": "Thank you, sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.5,
      "end": 95.0,
      "text": "Appreciate you, man."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.2,
      "end": 95.7,
      "text": "Have a great day."
    }
